{"tid":1071153,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"HBO 於全球秘密隱藏 6 只《Game of Thrones》鐵王座","createTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T08:01:04.000Z","uid":135867,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"459acd66aa74326a35d9925930df2e9ee202da49","tid":1071153,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:56:50.000Z","msg":"隨著《Game of Thrones》最終季即將到來，除了角色海報、正式預告和各集播放長度等資訊以及和 adidas 的聯乘 UltraBOOST&nbsp;之外，HBO 今回更帶來另一慶祝活動，在全球各地隱藏了 6 個象徵維斯特洛大陸最高王權的真實尺寸鐵王座，目前已知的情報共有森林中和北極冰原等地理環境。同時為慶祝此活動，HBO 更找來劇中多名演員拍攝宣傳片，有興趣的讀者不妨即刻前往官方頁面了解更多資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iUZJiv5PiUM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiUZJiv5PiUM&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3AexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=8bab31c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iUZJiv5PiUM</a>"},{"pid":"f349c0ff99be3b35de3a8270dcc4ec3fb91aad29","tid":1071153,"uid":208722,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T07:11:20.000Z","msg":"「只」"},{"pid":"323ccadc212aa75ebb8f157e59e8702b8a979da3","tid":1071153,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"有時都想台灣人認真少少做校對"}]}